readable.content: A child with her head in a cut out of a cow . A girl is poking her head through a cow cutout . A young boy is sticking his head through a cow face with a hole cut out of it . A young girl is putting her face in a cow cut-out at a farm . With a barn in the background a child puts her head through a hole in a cow cutout and smiles for the camera .
